{"tid":2059863,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"外國留學問題","createTime":"2020-06-11T08:22:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T09:10:47.000Z","uid":302501,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"64af7e8f2256dd55d0782416803f5d3bf2aa7810","tid":2059863,"uid":302501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T08:22:56.000Z","msg":"今年yr1<br />\n家境還可以<br />\n勉強支持到我去外國讀書<br />\n老母日日send d升學資料比我<br />\n日日chur9我<br />\n但係真心唔想過去外國讀書<br />\n一黎要拋低香港d野真係唔捨得<br />\n隻狗又老好容易無啦啦就過身<br />\n我屋企d老人家呢排成日出入醫院 <br />\n好驚陪唔到佢地最後一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有個拍拖幾年既女朋友 <br />\n好多野唔捨得<br />\n再加上宜家離開香港同個班拎bno走佬既廢佬無分別<br />\n唔想離開一個由細住到大既香港<br />\n背棄手足<br />\n大家有無d意見比到我 至少要應酬下我老母<br />\n利申老母深黃做開家長 但係覺得外國一定好過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97cfb5c0f80b83b79ce0a12a286b7b53841ae0a5","tid":2059863,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T08:23:46.000Z","msg":"邊個國家？讀咩？"},{"pid":"7856a1c52c0b0c44fcd66e34c54db90cd6345bd8","tid":2059863,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T08:24:07.000Z","msg":"點解講到好似移民咁...?"},{"pid":"99eae492565e3125b3a04960702cc304c72ccb3c","tid":2059863,"uid":165665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T08:26:35.000Z","msg":"幾歲啊 自己決定啦"},{"pid":"61aa4f823d6026c6b778f39f40f4fe58bec08542","tid":2059863,"uid":44210,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T08:27:21.000Z","msg":"講到你去讀書可以成世留係個度唔番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207ffb2bb6a0d7746d77ab0cc7e7a01bbaba01d7","tid":2059863,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T08:30:21.000Z","msg":"放假咪返黎囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb6f44445b3f63635005ae3463b8410be26243a0","tid":2059863,"uid":53117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T08:34:58.000Z","msg":"出去見識吓係好事，冇人叫你去讀書就變離地藍絲屌鳩香港人。屋企有能力送你出去更加要好好珍惜，唔好將眼光淨係放喺香港<br />\n你大多幾年出嚟做嘢就明，我都想當年大學可以出國讀"},{"pid":"e06f1be7589c18acfbb2c32bc0685f0fcb7e59ce","tid":2059863,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T08:38:15.000Z","msg":"你留係到啦 香港咁好做乜要去外國<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0204530985240d7ccd9c44e88e9051f3f0bec70f","tid":2059863,"uid":327622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T08:39:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd175357dc1b3d14987fd7e9d0ffdfbadc00b255","tid":2059863,"uid":327622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T08:40:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d29bbc9b0e6ff5613fcefe73e21c0025f76df26","tid":2059863,"uid":287577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T09:10:47.000Z","msg":"做嘜鳩姐，攞槍指住你咩？"}]}